title: Cisco Meraki: Organization API response codes
agents: cisco_meraki
catalog: os/services
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check plug-in monitors API response codes.

 In order to make this check plug-in work, you have to configure the ruleset for
 the special agent {{Cisco Meraki}} to include the "API response codes" section.

discovery:
 One service per organisation ID is created.

